description.short: DevFest 2025: Building Safe, Secure and Scalable Solutions with AI and Cloud. Experience DevFest Prayagraj 2025 - where innovation meets the rich heritage of Prayagraj. Join us as we blend cutting-edge technology with local culture, bringing the spirit of collaboration, knowledge, and growth to the heart of the Sangam city. Let's build the future of technology, rooted in values and driven by purpose.

whatToExpect.title: Networking Opportunities
whatToExpect.description: Connect with like-minded developers, industry leaders, and Google experts to expand your professional network and collaborate on projects.

whatToExpect.title: Career Guidance
whatToExpect.description: Get advice from industry professionals and Google experts on how to advance your career in tech, including resume reviews, interview tips, and career paths.

whatToExpect.title: Community Engagement
whatToExpect.description: Engage with the vibrant Google Developer Groups community, participate in interactive sessions, and explore ways to contribute to open-source projects.

pastDevFest.summery: DevFest 2024, organized by GDG Prayagraj, was a major tech event that brought together developers, tech enthusiasts, and industry experts for a day of learning and networking. The event featured insightful sessions on cutting-edge technologies, workshops, and hands-on coding activities. It provided an excellent platform for participants to explore topics like AI, cloud computing, and web development. DevFest 2023 fostered community engagement and inspired developers to innovate, collaborate, and grow within the tech ecosystem.
